y blatant gaps in time which aren't accounted for in your 12 second duration 3 second casting time scenario. I'm sure I wasn't twisting &quot;foodsong/bindsite/enduringbreath/60 slowdot/amplification twist. &quot;, as foodsong and bindsite weren't available when I played, and 60 slowdot and amplification, I simply didn't have- being 57 when I quit.<br>
<br>
